  <title>Cogl.StereoMode</title>
  <p>Represents how draw should affect the two buffers
of a stereo framebuffer. See <link xref="Cogl.Framebuffer.set_stereo_mode"/>.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>StereoMode.BOTH</code></title>
  <p>draw to both stereo buffers</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>StereoMode.LEFT</code></title>
  <p>draw only to the left stereo buffer</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>StereoMode.RIGHT</code></title>
  <p>draw only to the left stereo buffer</p>
</item>
